Forces each player to play the tank at least once before Map change.

-convars-
"tank_control_disable", "0", "if set 1, no Forces each player to play the tank at once,1=disabled"

-commands-
  *for adm
    !settankplayer <player> --> "force this player will become the tank"
    !clearteam --> "clear who_has_been_tank_arraylist for both team, useful when map change."
	
  *for everyone
	!tank
	!boss
	!t
